## 6. Detailed Feature Specifications for Claude Code CLI

### Feature: Smart Context Switching
**Logic**:
```typescript
// Pseudo-code for Context Watcher
onWindowChange((window) => {
  if (window.app === 'VS Code') {
    const repo = getGitRepo(window.title);
    const project = db.projects.find(p => p.repoPath === repo);
    if (project && currentTimer.project !== project) {
      notifyUser(`Switch timer to ${project.name}?`);
    }
  }
});
```

### Feature: The "Focus Shield"
**Description**: When a timer tagged "Deep Work" is running:
1.  Enable "Do Not Disturb" on OS (via CLI command).
2.  Block specific websites (via host file or browser extension).
3.  Play ambient noise (optional).

